      "firm_id": "optimistic_5",
      "description": "Looking for a budget-friendly project or a source for quality parts? This vehicle is in poor condition and needs some serious TLC, but it\u2019s an exciting opportunity for someone handy! Whether you're looking for a fixer-upper or a donor car, this is your chance to snag a deal and give it a new purpose!",
